                {% include 'component/icons/circle-checked.njk' %}
                <span>福利厚生の導入には運用の手間とコストがかかりそう</span>
              </li>
              <li class="card-description__detail">
                {% include 'component/icons/circle-checked.njk' %}
                <span>社内の業務負担を軽減したい</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <div class="circle-with-arrow">
              <div class="arrow-down"></div>
            </div>
          </a>
        </li>
        <li class="card-type6">
          <a href="#benefits" class="card">
            <div class="ttl-quaternary-container">
              <h4 class="ttl-quaternary">福利厚生を導入しているが
                <br />
                あまり使われていない
              </h4>
            </div>
            <div class="card-image">
              <img src="/assets/img/common/img-welfare-003.png" alt="">
            </div>
            <ul class="card-description">
              <li class="card-description__detail">
                {% include 'component/icons/circle-checked.njk' %}
                <span>利用率が低く、使う人が偏ってしまっている</span>
              </li>
              <li class="card-description__detail">
                {% include 'component/icons/circle-checked.njk' %}
                <span>多くの従業員に使ってもらえる福利厚生がほしい</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <div class="circle-with-arrow">
              <div class="arrow-down"></div>
            </div>
          </a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-secondary fadein">
    <div class="container-1200">
      <h2 class="ttl-secondary">「セゾンフクリコ」がまとめて解決します。</h2>

